this kind of our process

00:37:40.320 --> 00:37:41.600
for doing that,

00:37:42.639 --> 00:37:44.159
the indexing of work products

00:37:44.159 --> 00:37:44.800
and stuff like that.

00:37:47.600 --> 00:37:49.280
That'd be great to maybe share

