for your own situation?

00:39:09.199 --> 00:39:10.800
It's essentially like a function,

00:39:10.800 --> 00:39:12.639
but it's a more of a kind of open code.

00:39:16.399 --> 00:39:18.080
Those are super helpful, Mike.

